stories_text_raw:
As a user, I want to upload a submission, so that I can submit data for processing.
As an agency user, I want to validate my flex fields, so that I can ensure my data meets the necessary criteria before submission.
As a broker, I want to add users, so that I can manage their submissions and access.
As a broker, I want to prevent duplicate publishing of submissions, so that I can maintain data integrity and avoid errors.
As a broker, I want to process deletions for a given date, so that I can manage outdated or irrelevant data.
As a broker, I want to get a list of published FABS files, so that I can review and access successful submissions.
As a user, I want to publish a submission if it is validated, so that others can access the finalized data.
As a validator, I want to validate DUNS records, so that I can ensure that submissions contain valid identifiers.
As a validator, I want to validate required fields in a record, so that I can ensure all necessary information is provided for compliance.
As a broker, I want to upload and validate files, so that I can systematically manage new data submissions.
